Banking & Finance Associate, Magic Circle Firm, Dubai
Banking & Finance Associate, Magic Circle Firm, Dubai
Location:  --Dubai
This Magic Circle firm with an outstanding client base is looking for a junior to mid-level lawyer (2-4 PQE) for their Dubai office.
The role will be a great opportunity to work a range matters in the team, covering different types of high quality work.The team has expanded over the last few years and they are still extremely busy, hence the needs for additional hires to handle a broad mix of finance work.
The successful candidate will have excellent academics and have trained at another Magic Circle/top US firm. UAE experience is highly desirable but not essential.
Should you wish to apply for this role, please contact Richard McLerie by sending your cv through to richard@jlegal.com.
